          |     &lt;span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill"&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;
          |   &lt;/li&gt;
          | &lt;/ol&gt;

      h4 Horizontal
      p Add <code>.list-group-horizontal</code> to change the layout of list group items from vertical to horizontal across all breakpoints. Alternatively, choose a responsive variant <code>.list-group-horizontal-{sm|md|lg|xl|xxl}</code> to make a list group horizontal starting at that breakpoint's <code>min-width</code>. Currently <strong>horizontal list groups cannot be combined with flush list groups</strong>.
      p <strong>ProTip:</strong> Want equal-width list group items when horizontal? Add <code>.flex-fill</code> to each list group item.

      .bd-example
