      h4 Checkboxes and radios
      p Place Bootstrap's checkboxes and radios within list group items and customize as needed. You can use them without <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>s, but please remember to include an <code>aria-label</code> attribute and value for accessibility.

      .bd-example
        ul.list-group
          li.list-group-item
            input#firstCheckbox.form-check-input.me-1(type='checkbox' value='')
            label.form-check-label(for='firstCheckbox') First checkbox
          li.list-group-item
            input#secondCheckbox.form-check-input.me-1(type='checkbox' value='')
            label.form-check-label(for='secondCheckbox') Second checkbox
          li.list-group-item
            input#thirdCheckbox.form-check-input.me-1(type='checkbox' value='')
            label.form-check-label(for='thirdCheckbox') Third checkbox

      pre
        code.language-html
